{"tid":1164840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國客遊日狂挖生蠔極擾民　專家：含大量毒素不宜食用","createTime":"2019-05-21T11:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T21:45:25.000Z","uid":66271,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f779f7de8917cca91fb93c46b8a768baa35d4884","tid":1164840,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"日本是中國人常到的旅遊熱點，但近年他們似乎有新的遊日行程，就是挖生蠔！據日本東京電視台節目《ありえへん&infin;世界》報導，在日本千葉縣江戶川河口一帶，經常有中國遊客前往挖生蠔，行為不止影響當地居民，日本專家也指出該地區的生蠔含有毒素，食用會非常危險。<br />\n<br />\n節目中可以看到中國遊客帶齊所有挖蠔裝備，如手套、開蠔刀、網、桶等等，都是有備而來的大量採蠔。其中一位受訪的中國大叔更表示，比起鄰近的迪士尼樂園，他認為挖蠔更有趣，日本人不挖這些野生蠔簡直是浪費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/20190519144251__e89ea2e5b995e688aae59c96202019-05-1920e4b88be58d881.25.10_12571288795ce3758001c66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F20190519144251__e89ea2e5b995e688aae59c96202019-05-1920e4b88be58d881.25.10_12571288795ce3758001c66.jpg&h=37b3f6f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是中國人在瘋狂採掘生蠔後，只帶走蠔肉，而蠔殼就隨處丟棄，令當地居民相當不滿，而且要「執手尾」。鋒利的蠔殼亦曾經令數位當地小孩受傷需要送院，當地已立下不少簡體字告示牌呼籲中國遊客要帶走蠔殼，但情況似乎並沒有改善。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/-2019-05-21-11.31.36_3418157785ce37586f089b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F-2019-05-21-11.31.36_3418157785ce37586f089b.png&h=4f6bf5aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"006472a3b68f096dfdc14bd49b16d5fbadb599c7","tid":1164840,"uid":228955,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"食死佢地 好事"},{"pid":"a1751fcacf85e23c0af21d61859a726ccc932f3b","tid":1164840,"uid":153827,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"006472a3b68f096dfdc14bd49b16d5fbadb599c7","tid":1164840,"uid":228955,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"食死佢地 好事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"元素抗性100% ,冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab5535472ff4eac9c3ae34bc8b2efcc5ee25a5c","tid":1164840,"uid":57787,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"006472a3b68f096dfdc14bd49b16d5fbadb599c7","tid":1164840,"uid":228955,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"食死佢地 好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:55:45.000Z","msg":"本土嘅毒素已經有晒抗體，係時候練海外嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5608c50cae9054dbfb1bee1d26f8cbe18d8c6cd","tid":1164840,"uid":45376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"你同佢地定啦專家"},{"pid":"da6c5d14066846537a6ac707ae987258d5e29f79","tid":1164840,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1751fcacf85e23c0af21d61859a726ccc932f3b","tid":1164840,"uid":153827,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"006472a3b68f096dfdc14bd49b16d5fbadb599c7","tid":1164840,"uid":228955,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"食死佢地 好事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"元素抗性100% ,冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"元素週期表護體，百毒不侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83115572551f13df92a476ad089a1a4759049d56","tid":1164840,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dd7b8e11087011906dafd954947d1b8384a19a","tid":1164840,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"呢個地球冇民族厚顏無恥得過支那人"},{"pid":"cb40fcdcfd23c5be0fb46cdad7aad88c8b46ce34","tid":1164840,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:52:31.000Z","msg":"遲下世界又黎多次排華"},{"pid":"49